.01$) by +1dB in Signal to Distortion Ratio (SDR)\nand +1.5dB in Signal to Interference Ratio (SIR).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Nov 2021 17:25:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-17"}
