e Protostellar\nInterferometric Line Survey of IRAS 16293-2422 using ALMA. CD$_3$OH is securely\ndetected in the data, with a large number of clearly separated and\nwell-reproduced lines. We detected lines belonging to the ground and the first\nexcited torsional states. The derived abundance of CD$_3$OH relative to\nnon-deuterated isotopolog confirm the significant enhancement of this multiply\ndeuterated variant. This finding is in line with other observations of multiply\ndeuterated complex organic molecules and may serve as an important constraint\non their formation models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Nov 2021 11:53:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-14"}
